{
  "stem": "5883.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That-- because that time, no fence was no more.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you couldn't tell where really the house was, if it was before in the ghetto or was not.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was in the wintertime.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1945.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we stayed there for a while.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And at that time, my brother-- who's not really my brother-- came to us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The way he came to us, he worked at a farmer's, you know, place.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He had a farm.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the man knew my mother.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The man from the farm, he was Christian.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He came one day.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he told my mother that he has a young man, and he would like to give him up.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So my mother told him to bring him over, and she will take him in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So he brought him over.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He was by that time maybe 13 years old-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] 13 or 14, something like that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And at first the young man didn't want to stay with us because he only knew the farmer.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So my mother told him that-- not to be afraid.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He couldn't speak Jewish nor Polish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He, he spoke Russian.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And just to try it out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So he decided to, to stay with us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His name is Mike.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he-- we didn't really have enough furniture in the house where we could put him to sleep.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So me and my sisters gave up our bed, and we slept on the floor in the same room to watch him so he wouldn't run away from us.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he got used to us, and then he told us how he got liberated.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What happened, he and his mother and father and his sister-- and they took the Jews in his hometown together.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
